{"tid":628116,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)A計劃1-2 龍兄虎弟 飛鷹計劃","createTime":"2018-04-13T14:03:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T19:01:41.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b25232db630eb31e11705bf7a29ca59b059de845","tid":628116,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:03:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=7Mc20amBNTh%2BozCldboKEPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=ffb54945\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=7Mc20amBNTh%2BozCldboKEPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=698a04dc\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=7Mc20amBNTh%2BozCldboKEPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=04b11f41\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/40/Project_A_film_poster_(Original_Hong_Kong_Version).jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F40%2FProject_A_film_poster_%28Original_Hong_Kong_Version%29.jpg&h=343ee6da&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/8/8a/Armour_of_God.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F8%2F8a%2FArmour_of_God.jpg&h=42a5906f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7c/Armour-of-god-II-poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7c%2FArmour-of-god-II-poster.jpg&h=34e80fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.香港開埠初期，海盜橫行，在香港的海面，盜魁羅三炮與奸商周永齡互相勾結，深悉貨運情報，因而無往不利，官府亦為之束手。水警沙展馬如龍對官府政策非常不滿，憤而辭職，與卓一飛合謀對付海盜，卓一飛雖然武功高強，可惜他唯利是圖，他與馬如龍合作騙取軍火，旨在從中圖利。羅三炮勢力龐大，馬如龍和卓一飛二人屢剿失利。馬如龍心有不甘，重新加入水師警隊，與上司洪天賜、卓一飛三人合力喬裝闖入匪巢，終於將海盜一網打盡。<br />\n<br />\n2.清朝末年的香港，在上、中、西環有「鎮三環」之稱的幫辦暗中勾結西環惡霸勾心虎，西環治安一時烏煙瘴氣。警官馬如龍（成龍）奉命接管西環後，迅速將勾心虎拘捕人獄，招來「鎮三環」的怨恨。 彼時內地革命風雲翻湧，革命黨人來港宣傳，併計劃營救被捕同志。為將革命黨人一網打盡，清廷派遣密使聯絡鎮三環，馬如龍結識白影紅、瑩瑩、珊珊等革命黨人（張曼玉、關之琳、劉嘉玲等）後也被捲入鬥爭漩渦，而同時，一群四肢發達頭腦簡單的海盜正在伺機向馬如龍報仇.......<br />\n<br />\n3.基督教《聖經》中記載有五件「上帝武裝」曾經打敗邪魔，後來散失在世界各地。伯爵得到了其中的三件，而邪魔的傳人得到了兩件，艾楠的女友羅娜和艾楠在時裝表演時，羅娜被邪魔假扮的僧侶抓走，贖回條件就是要三件上帝武裝。艾楠只得找兄弟飛鷹幫忙.......<br />\n<br />\n4.故事講述第二次世界大戰納粹德軍於非洲沙漠隱藏了數百噸黃金，飛鷹Jackie與助手Ada、德國少女Elsa及桃子一行人受命尋找。他們千辛萬苦到達藏金地點，但這裡不只有黃金，還有一連串未解之謎等著他們...<br />\n<br />\n10 15PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=7Mc20amBNTh%2BozCldboKEPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=1a640449\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=7Mc20amBNTh%2BozCldboKEPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=ac5d7ef4\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cf40f0bc873e4b6104e2e377eb61194898c100","tid":628116,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:10:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f115c3c99f9301e2ed89f445223a5dd09d2585a3","tid":628116,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T14:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38edeff2fd4620bb8e1ffca0c97e4f8369937f7e","tid":628116,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:23:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88ed21440c16b77cff4e72fd687a9d901f2bab13","tid":628116,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T15:53:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeebc6c2db01661823da211dffce2b2ac7547f60","tid":628116,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T17:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e64d8bae0545a0ff293502452a56aef4423a50","tid":628116,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-13T17:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a14e4799a2e15502d17bbf9f5d5d15062fc5ae","tid":628116,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit